title: Luxer One Package Lockers, Smart Home Technology, Patio
posting_body: ['The Landing at Mansfield Apartments is the apartment you’ve been looking for in Mansfield, Texas.', 'With comfortable one-, two-, and three-bedroom homes complete with washers and dryers, private patios, and kitchen pantries, you’re guaranteed to find a place to live with a lifestyle to love.', 'What’s more, as a member of the community you’ll also have access to our outdoor grilling stations and resort-style swimming pool, all conveniently located near shopping and dining at Mansfield Towne Crossing.', 'Find a home at The Landing at Mansfield Apartments, where living more is the new standard.', '-Resident', 'Clubhouse w/ Coffee Bar', '-Billiards & Shuffleboard', '-Double Sided Kitchen Sinks w/ Gooseneck Faucet', '-Garages', '-On-Site Professional Management', '-Rapid-Response Maintenance', '-Custom Wood-Finish Cabinetry', '-Patio', '-Online Rent Payment & Service Requests', '-Covered Parking Available', '-Luxer One Package Lockers', '-Internet Cafe', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Pricing and availability subject to change.', 'Equal housing opportunity.']
